description: [``botocore``] Custom Orchestration API release for AWSBedrockAgents.
[``botocore``] Custom Orchestration and Streaming configurations API release for AWSBedrockAgents.
[``botocore``] Enables access to ValueMap and ValueInteger types for SegmentAttributes and fixes deserialization bug for DescribeContactFlow in AmazonConnect Public API

[``botocore``] Adds support for Time-based Copy for EBS Snapshots and Cross Region PrivateLink. Time-based Copy ensures that EBS Snapshots are copied within and across AWS Regions in a specified timeframe. Cross Region PrivateLink enables customers to connect to VPC endpoint services hosted in other AWS Regions.
[``botocore``] Private sharing, file upload and data collection feature support for Q Apps
